Tests the update while it is collecting data from the sensors and sending data to the PI system.
The snaps should be stored in the local file system using a tree like the following under ${TMP_DIRECTORY} :

    snaps
        x86_64
            foglamp.info
            foglamp_1.1.3_amd64.snap
            foglamp_1.1.4_amd64.snap

'foglamp.info' contains the information regarding the latest version available, in the previous example :

    foglamp@foglamp-core:~/tmp/snaps/x86_64$ cat foglamp.info
    1.1.4

